library(ggplot2)

# Generate data
x <- seq(0, 2*pi, length.out = 100)
y <- sin(x)

# Create the plot
ggplot(data.frame(x, y), aes(x, y)) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(title = "Sine Wave", x = "x", y = "sin(x)")
